{"thag4.1:0.1":"Theragatha 4.1 ","thag4.1:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","thag4.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag4.1:0.4":"Nagasamalattheragatha ","thag4.1:1.1":"“Alankata suvasana, ","thag4.1:1.2":"malini candanussada; ","thag4.1:1.3":"Majjhe mahapathe nari, ","thag4.1:1.4":"turiye naccati nattaki. ","thag4.1:2.1":"Pindikaya pavitthoham, ","thag4.1:2.2":"gacchanto nam udikkhisam; ","thag4.1:2.3":"Alankatam suvasanam, ","thag4.1:2.4":"maccupasamva odditam. ","thag4.1:3.1":"Tato me manasikaro, ","thag4.1:3.2":"yoniso udapajjatha; ","thag4.1:3.3":"Adinavo paturahu, ","thag4.1:3.4":"nibbida samatitthatha. ","thag4.1:4.1":"Tato cittam vimucci me, ","thag4.1:4.2":"passa dhammasudhammatam; ","thag4.1:4.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag4.1:4.4":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thag4.1:4.5":"… Nagasamalo thero …. "}